Instead of [this](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/2ba44607fe09c4fb98a52ca2149b0c9869a87b4c/src/libterm/terminfo/parm.rs#L119-L133):

``` rust
                        if !stack.is_empty() {
                            match stack.pop().unwrap() {
                                ...
                            }
                        } else {
                            ...
                        }
```

do:

``` rust
                        match stack.pop() {
                            Some(..) => ...
                            None => ...
                        }
```

---

Similarly, instead of [this](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/2ba44607fe09c4fb98a52ca2149b0c9869a87b4c/src/libterm/terminfo/parm.rs#L151-L158):

``` rust
                        if stack.len() > 1 {
                            match (stack.pop().unwrap(), stack.pop().unwrap()) {
                                (Number(y), Number(x)) => ...
                                _ => ...
                            }
                        } else {
                            ...
                        }
```

do:

``` rust
                        match (stack.pop(), stack.pop()) {
                            (Some(Number(y)), Some(Number(x))) => ...
                            (Some(_), Some(_) => ...
                            _ => ...
                        }
```

There are multiple instances of these patterns in this file so make sure to clean up all of them
